msgstr ""
"Cedwir cofnodion sylfaenol gan wasanaeth Casglu Data'r Arolwg am gyfnod o"
" 30 niwrnod. Gellir cadw digwyddiadau arbennig am gyfnod hwy."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:467
msgid ""
"Our general retention period for data collected via annual surveys is 3 "
"years."
msgstr ""
"Ein cyfnod cadw cyffredinol ar gyfer data a gesglir drwy arolygon "
"blynyddol yw 3 blynedd. "

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:469
msgid ""
"Personal data used for account access will be retained as long as the "
"account is active."
msgstr ""
"Cedwir data personol a ddefnyddir ar gyfer mynediad i gyfrif cyhyd ag y "
"bo'r cyfrif yn weithredol."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:471
msgid "Your rights over your personal data"
msgstr "Eich hawliau dros eich data personol"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:473
msgid ""
"The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) details eight rights of "
"individuals"
msgstr ""
"Mae'r Rheoliad Diogelu Data Cyffredinol (GDPR) yn rhoi manylion wyth hawl"
" sydd gan unigolion"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:475
msgid "The right to be informed"
msgstr "Yr hawl i gael eu hysbysu"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:476
msgid "The right of access"
msgstr "Yr hawl mynediad"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:477
msgid "The right to rectification"
msgstr "Yr hawl i gywiro"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:478
msgid "The right to erasure"
msgstr "Yr hawl i ddileu"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:479
msgid "The right to restrict processing"
msgstr "Yr hawl i gyfyngu ar brosesu"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:480
msgid "The right to data portability"
msgstr "Yr hawl i gludadwyedd data"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:480
msgid ""
"This right only exists if the lawful basis used is either consent or "
"contract. Neither the Survey Data Collection service nor any surveys "
"hosted on this platform rely on either of the lawful basis and therefore "
"this right is not applicable."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r hawl hwn yn bodoli’n unig os yw’r sail gyfreithiol a ddefnyddir yn "
"naill ai’n ganiatâd neu’n gytundeb. Nid yw naill ai gwasanaeth Casglu "
"Data’r Arolwg neu unrhyw arolygon a geir ar y llwyfan hwn yn dibynnu ar y"
" naill neu'r llall o’r sail gyfreithiol ac felly nid yw’r hawl hwn yn "
"gymwys."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:481
msgid "The right to object"
msgstr "Yr hawl i wrthwynebu"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:482
msgid "Rights in relation to automated decision making and profiling."
msgstr "Hawliau sy'n gysylltiedig â gwneud penderfyniadau awtomatig a phroffilio."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:482
msgid "No automated decision making or profiling occurs at the personal level."
msgstr ""
"Nid oes unrhyw wneud penderfyniadau awtomatig neu broffilio'n digwydd ar "
"y lefel bersonol."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:484
msgid "These rights are subject to exemptions."
msgstr "Mae'r hawliau hyn yn amodol ar eithriadau."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:487
msgid "Contacting the Data Protection Office"
msgstr "Cysylltu â'r Swyddfa Diogelu Data"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:489
msgid ""
"The Data Protection Officer for the Office for National Statistics can be"
" contacted as follows"
msgstr ""
"Gellir cysylltu â'r Swyddog Diogelu Data ar gyfer y Swyddfa Ystadegau "
"Cenedlaethol fel a ganlyn"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:497
msgid "Contacting the Information Commissioner’s Office"
msgstr "Cysylltu â Swyddfa'r Comisiynydd Gwybodaeth"

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:499
msgid ""
"We welcome the opportunity to be able to answer any questions or concerns"
" you may have around the information provided here. If you are unhappy "
"with our response to any of your requests or you have concerns around how"
" your data has been handled, you have the right to lodge a complaint with"
" the Information Commissioner’s Office."
msgstr ""
"Rydym yn croesawu’r cyfle i fedru ateb unrhyw gwestiynau neu bryderon a "
"allai fod gennych ynghylch y wybodaeth a ddarperir yma. Os byddwch yn "
"anhapus gyda’n hymateb i unrhyw un o’ch ceisiadau neu os bydd gennych "
"bryderon ynghylch sut y trafodwyd eich data, mae gennych yr hawl i gwyno "
"i Swyddfa’r Comisiynydd Gwybodaeth."

#: templates/static/cookies-privacy.html:507
msgid ""
"The Information Commissioner’s Office provides guidance to the public on "
"raising a concern with an organisation at the following location"
msgstr ""
"Mae Swyddfa'r Comisiynydd Gwybodaeth yn darparu canllawiau i'r cyhoedd ar"
" godi pryder gyda sefydliad yn y lleoliad canlynol"

